Response to
Episode 7 - "The Clean Room"
@-------------------------------------------------
        Patterson's persistence is something admirable. He relentlessly attempts
a problem, until he succeeds. I think the reason why Mr. Brown wants us to
watch this is to make us realize that sometimes, a problem requires many
different approaches before it can finally be solved. I was confused at first
when the mysterious killer was described, but lead eventually revealed itself
